1
00:00:14,040 --> 00:00:16,440
Tak sangka, anak cemerlang dalam legenda,

2
00:00:16,710 --> 00:00:18,670
Tuan Muda Zhuge
daripada keluarga Zhuge negara Yong

3
00:00:18,670 --> 00:00:20,330
boleh jatuh sampai tahap ini.

4
00:00:20,550 --> 00:00:20,870
Bukankah dia

5
00:00:20,870 --> 00:00:23,200
pengintip yang paling ditakutkan orang?

6
00:00:23,440 --> 00:00:25,640
Kenapa boleh dicedera parah macam ini?

7
00:00:29,670 --> 00:00:30,390
Xing Er,

8
00:00:31,120 --> 00:00:32,980
saya tahu awak ada banyak soalan,

9
00:00:33,240 --> 00:00:35,370
saya juga patut beri awak penjelasan.

10
00:00:35,390 --> 00:00:37,190
Namun, saya ada sebab diri saya.

11
00:00:37,280 --> 00:00:39,740
Awak tunggu saya selesaikan semua perkara.

12
00:00:44,520 --> 00:00:45,390
Zhuge Yue,

13
00:00:46,560 --> 00:00:48,690
boleh awak tinggal di sini untuk saya?

14
00:00:51,430 --> 00:00:52,070
Ya,

15
00:00:52,430 --> 00:00:53,430
betul cakap awak.

16
00:00:55,030 --> 00:00:56,470
Namun ini hal saya,

17
00:00:56,920 --> 00:00:58,520
ia tiada kaitan dengan awak.

18
00:01:13,710 --> 00:01:16,910
Saya langsung tak sedar
kesabaran dan penderitaan awak.

19
00:01:17,120 --> 00:01:18,950
Saya malah selalu marah akan awak,

20
00:01:18,950 --> 00:01:19,810
salahkan awak,

21
00:01:20,070 --> 00:01:21,510
tapi tak pernah terfikir,

22
00:01:21,510 --> 00:01:23,640
rupanya awak dah alami
begitu banyak penderitaan.

23
00:01:23,640 --> 00:01:25,310
Kalau dia sengaja tak beritahu puteri,

24
00:01:25,310 --> 00:01:26,440
takut puteri risau,

25
00:01:26,880 --> 00:01:28,680
sudah tentu puteri takkan tahu.

26
00:01:43,740 --> 00:01:45,430
Racun yang dikenanya sangat pelik.

27
00:01:45,430 --> 00:01:47,280
Ia melilit sepanjang meridian jantung
dan merebak ke seluruh anggota badan,

28
00:01:47,280 --> 00:01:48,479
namun bergerak halus
seperti benang sutera.

29
00:01:48,479 --> 00:01:50,789
Saya dah cuba sedaya upaya,
tapi tak dapat keluarkannya.

30
00:01:50,789 --> 00:01:53,000
Saya hanya boleh gunakan jarum
untuk tutup titik akupunkturnya dulu

31
00:01:53,000 --> 00:01:55,789
untuk melindungi
organ dalamannya daripada tercedera.

32
00:01:55,789 --> 00:01:57,229
Tapi berapa lama ia dapat bertahan,

33
00:01:57,229 --> 00:01:58,710
itu bergantung pada
kekuatan dalamannya sendiri.

34
00:01:58,710 --> 00:01:59,280
Puteri,

35
00:01:59,430 --> 00:02:01,000
bagaimana dengan rancangan kita

36
00:02:01,000 --> 00:02:02,070
untuk menyelamatkan Panglima He kali ini?

37
00:02:02,070 --> 00:02:03,470
Masa kita dah tak banyak.

38
00:02:04,200 --> 00:02:05,120
Sekarang,

39
00:02:05,790 --> 00:02:06,950
kita hanya boleh tunggu He Xiao

40
00:02:06,950 --> 00:02:08,520
diserahkan kepada Tentera Helang Hitam,

41
00:02:08,520 --> 00:02:12,210
semasa dalam perjalanan pulang ke Yanbei,
kita cari peluang untuk menyelamatkannya.

42
00:02:12,210 --> 00:02:15,870
Esok saya akan pergi meninjau
keadaan dengan Fang Miaomiao dulu.

43
00:03:35,770 --> 00:03:40,950
[REBIRTH]

44
00:03:41,620 --> 00:03:44,010
[Episod 15]

45
00:03:44,040 --> 00:03:44,960
[Kota Lin]

46
00:03:56,430 --> 00:03:58,030
Nanti, apabila Tentera Yong buka gerbang,

47
00:03:58,030 --> 00:04:00,490
tawanan perang Yanbei keluar dari gerbang,

48
00:04:01,150 --> 00:04:02,480
kita pun boleh pastikan

49
00:04:02,840 --> 00:04:03,900
kedudukan He Xiao.

50
00:04:04,520 --> 00:04:05,680
Buka gerbang!

51
00:04:40,860 --> 00:04:41,920
Mereka dah datang.

52
00:04:48,880 --> 00:04:49,510
He Xiao.

53
00:04:53,330 --> 00:04:55,040
Habis, kita dah terperangkap!

54
00:04:55,040 --> 00:04:56,500
Cepat tutup gerbang kota!

55
00:04:56,850 --> 00:04:57,380
Cepat!

56
00:05:05,950 --> 00:05:07,040
Bunuh!

57
00:05:13,680 --> 00:05:14,510
Bunyi apa itu?

58
00:05:15,040 --> 00:05:15,950
Pastinya berlaku sesuatu.

59
00:05:15,950 --> 00:05:18,010
Awak baring dulu, saya pergi tolong.

60
00:05:58,990 --> 00:05:59,830
[He Xiao, Panglima Tentera Anggun]

61
00:05:59,260 --> 00:06:00,060
Panglima Chu!

62
00:06:03,140 --> 00:06:03,790
Naik kuda!

63
00:06:03,820 --> 00:06:04,380
Ya!

64
00:06:05,510 --> 00:06:06,770
Tahan mereka bertiga!

65
00:06:07,110 --> 00:06:08,970
Jangan biarkan mereka terlepas!

66
00:06:26,510 --> 00:06:28,160
He Xiao, Miao, kamu pergi dulu,

67
00:06:28,160 --> 00:06:28,680
saya akan uruskan di belakang.

68
00:06:28,680 --> 00:06:29,630
Tuan, jangan!

69
00:06:29,630 --> 00:06:30,360
Ini arahan!

70
00:06:30,360 --> 00:06:30,870
Puteri!

71
00:06:30,950 --> 00:06:31,510
Pergi!

72
00:07:40,870 --> 00:07:41,530
Cepat lari!

73
00:07:58,870 --> 00:07:59,480
Cepat pergi!

74
00:07:59,480 --> 00:08:01,360
Tuan Muda!

75
00:08:01,830 --> 00:08:02,750
Tuan Muda!

76
00:08:04,350 --> 00:08:05,030
Tuan Muda!

77
00:08:05,050 --> 00:08:07,020
Ini saya, saya Shiyi!

78
00:08:05,480 --> 00:08:06,940
[Yue Shiyi, Tentera Pengawal Yue
Pusat Gunung Hijau]

79
00:08:07,160 --> 00:08:07,830
Shiyi?

80
00:08:08,870 --> 00:08:09,560
Tuan Muda!

81
00:08:10,430 --> 00:08:11,080
Shiyi.

82
00:08:12,780 --> 00:08:14,110
Kenapa kamu ada di sini?

83
00:08:33,549 --> 00:08:34,270
Chu.

84
00:08:42,200 --> 00:08:42,870
Chu.

85
00:08:44,630 --> 00:08:45,760
Ikut saya baliklah.

86
00:08:46,440 --> 00:08:47,640
Kita balik ke Yanbei.

87
00:08:48,030 --> 00:08:48,720
Yan Xun,

88
00:08:50,020 --> 00:08:51,620
hubungan kita dah berakhir.

89
00:08:57,000 --> 00:08:57,630
Chu,

90
00:08:58,510 --> 00:09:00,790
kita pernah harungi hidup
dan mati bersama,

91
00:09:00,790 --> 00:09:02,190
berkongsi suka dan duka.

92
00:09:03,000 --> 00:09:04,200
Saya tak percaya antara kita

93
00:09:04,200 --> 00:09:06,530
ada masalah
yang tak dapat diselesaikan.

94
00:09:06,870 --> 00:09:08,390
Kenapa awak begitu nekad?

95
00:09:08,790 --> 00:09:09,510
Yan Xun,

96
00:09:09,700 --> 00:09:11,430
kita pernah berjuang bersama,

97
00:09:11,840 --> 00:09:14,390
kita satu-satunya rakan seperjuangan
dan keluarga antara satu sama lain.

98
00:09:14,390 --> 00:09:15,240
Jalan yang pernah kita lalui bersama

99
00:09:15,240 --> 00:09:16,670
dah lama sampai ke penghujungnya.

100
00:09:16,670 --> 00:09:17,730
Cuba awak menoleh,

101
00:09:18,550 --> 00:09:20,750
kita dah lama menuju
ke haluan masing-masing.

102
00:09:20,750 --> 00:09:22,120
Saya berasal daripada golongan hamba,

103
00:09:22,120 --> 00:09:24,240
saya cuma nak hapuskan
perhambaan dan hentikan peperangan,

104
00:09:24,240 --> 00:09:25,960
buat orang yang nyawanya tak bernilai pun

105
00:09:25,960 --> 00:09:27,510
berhak untuk terus hidup.

106
00:09:27,810 --> 00:09:29,740
Namun, awak cuma nak balas dendam.

107
00:09:30,200 --> 00:09:31,720
Awak mahu terus gunakan darah baharu

108
00:09:31,720 --> 00:09:33,150
untuk bersihkan dendam keluarga

109
00:09:33,150 --> 00:09:34,320
dan dendam Yanbei!

110
00:09:34,320 --> 00:09:35,150
Chu!

111
00:09:36,500 --> 00:09:39,120
Dunia ini memang yang kuat
menindas yang lemah,

112
00:09:39,120 --> 00:09:40,870
tak pernah ada keadilan.

113
00:09:41,360 --> 00:09:42,490
Semasa keluarga Yan

114
00:09:42,790 --> 00:09:44,360
mati dengan tragis
di Platform Sembilan Neraka,

115
00:09:44,360 --> 00:09:45,560
di mana keadilannya?

116
00:09:46,200 --> 00:09:47,870
Semasa kita dikurung di Pusat Merdu

117
00:09:47,870 --> 00:09:48,720
dan tanpa pergantungan,

118
00:09:48,720 --> 00:09:49,790
di mana orang awam?

119
00:09:50,750 --> 00:09:53,550
Semasa saya hilang segala-galanya
dan putus asa,

120
00:09:54,010 --> 00:09:55,130
hanyalah awak yang

121
00:09:56,130 --> 00:09:57,210
ada di sisi saya.

122
00:09:59,200 --> 00:09:59,870
Chu.

123
00:10:01,270 --> 00:10:02,150
Bagi saya,

124
00:10:03,390 --> 00:10:04,120
dunia,

125
00:10:05,390 --> 00:10:06,150
keadilan,

126
00:10:07,800 --> 00:10:10,000
semua ini tak setanding hubungan kita.

127
00:10:10,200 --> 00:10:10,870
Yan Xun,

128
00:10:11,640 --> 00:10:12,500
saya tersilap.

129
00:10:13,150 --> 00:10:15,360
Dulu saya ingat
kita ada matlamat yang sama.

130
00:10:15,360 --> 00:10:17,320
Sebab kita saling bergantung
seperti bibir dan gigi.

131
00:10:17,320 --> 00:10:20,080
Jadi saya anggap awak orang
yang paling rapat dengan saya.

132
00:10:20,080 --> 00:10:21,940
Sekarang kita tak sehaluan lagi.

133
00:10:23,200 --> 00:10:24,860
Tolonglah lepaskan diri awak

134
00:10:25,390 --> 00:10:26,720
dan lepaskan saya juga.

135
00:10:47,200 --> 00:10:48,000
Chu,

136
00:10:49,790 --> 00:10:51,120
saya boleh jamin,

137
00:10:53,630 --> 00:10:55,360
awak tak dapat berjuang keluar

138
00:10:56,230 --> 00:10:57,870
dari sini seorang diri.

139
00:11:15,670 --> 00:11:16,600
Zhuge Yue.

140
00:11:16,960 --> 00:11:17,600
Yan Xun.

141
00:11:18,480 --> 00:11:20,540
Tak sangka kita akan bertemu begini.

142
00:11:21,440 --> 00:11:22,080
Xing Er,

143
00:11:22,750 --> 00:11:23,750
semalam awak kata

144
00:11:24,200 --> 00:11:25,460
nak saya sentiasa ada.

145
00:11:25,670 --> 00:11:27,200
Saya berjanji kepada awak.

146
00:11:27,390 --> 00:11:29,250
Saya juga mahu awak sentiasa ada.

147
00:11:29,630 --> 00:11:31,360
Tak kira di syurga atau neraka,

148
00:11:31,750 --> 00:11:32,950
kita sehidup semati.

149
00:11:34,430 --> 00:11:35,430
Zhuge Yue.

150
00:11:38,320 --> 00:11:40,920
Dulu awak memanah saya
di luar kota Zhenhuang,

151
00:11:41,440 --> 00:11:43,200
saya dah balas awak di tasik ais.

152
00:11:43,200 --> 00:11:44,910
Sekarang, kita dah
tak terhutang kepada sesama lain lagi.

153
00:11:44,910 --> 00:11:46,320
Jika awak pergi sekarang

154
00:11:46,840 --> 00:11:49,370
dan jangan campur tangan
urusan saya dan Chu,

155
00:11:49,790 --> 00:11:52,120
saya boleh anggap awak tak pernah datang.

156
00:11:52,360 --> 00:11:54,420
Urusan antara kita boleh dilupakan,

157
00:11:55,630 --> 00:11:57,600
tapi kalau awak masih berdegil,

158
00:11:58,510 --> 00:11:59,750
biarpun ayahanda awak...

159
00:11:59,750 --> 00:12:00,630
Diamlah!

160
00:12:01,870 --> 00:12:04,360
Awak tak layak untuk
menilai ayahanda saya langsung!

161
00:12:04,360 --> 00:12:05,870
Semua orang dengar arahan!

162
00:12:05,870 --> 00:12:07,870
Orang yang pancung kepala Zhuge Yue

163
00:12:08,720 --> 00:12:10,150
akan dilantik sebagai hulubalang!

164
00:12:10,150 --> 00:12:10,960
Baik!

165
00:12:34,590 --> 00:12:35,520
Mari kita pergi.

166
00:12:39,440 --> 00:12:40,050
Berundur!

167
00:12:54,600 --> 00:12:57,300
Maharaja kita seorang
yang bijaksana dan berani.

168
00:12:57,300 --> 00:12:59,840
Baginda ialah pemimpin
pilihan dewa-dewi Yanbei!

169
00:12:59,840 --> 00:13:00,390
Betul!

170
00:13:00,840 --> 00:13:01,640
Saya dah agak,

171
00:13:01,870 --> 00:13:02,480
maharaja kita

172
00:13:02,480 --> 00:13:04,240
berjaya menawan kota Lin

173
00:13:04,510 --> 00:13:06,200
dengan alasan pertukaran tawanan perang.

174
00:13:06,200 --> 00:13:08,360
Baginda berjaya memperdayakan
orang-orang Yong jahat itu.

175
00:13:08,360 --> 00:13:09,510
Tak lama lagi,

176
00:13:09,630 --> 00:13:11,720
baginda akan memimpin kita
menyerang kota Zhenhuang

177
00:13:11,720 --> 00:13:14,120
lalu membalas dendam untuk
saudara-saudara kita yang telah terkorban!

178
00:13:14,120 --> 00:13:15,720
Betul, balas dendam!

179
00:13:17,670 --> 00:13:18,320
Mari!

180
00:13:23,630 --> 00:13:24,870
Demi Yanbei kita,

181
00:13:26,200 --> 00:13:27,860
demi maharaja baharu Yanbei,

182
00:13:28,720 --> 00:13:29,380
bersulang.

183
00:13:29,840 --> 00:13:31,240
Menyulangi tuanku!

184
00:14:01,320 --> 00:14:01,960
Tuanku,

185
00:14:02,800 --> 00:14:05,630
patik dengar tuanku menawan kota Lin
dengan mengetuai Tentera Helang Hitam,

186
00:14:05,630 --> 00:14:06,720
patik datang khasnya untuk
mengucapkan tahniah kepada tuanku

187
00:14:06,720 --> 00:14:07,750
dan Yanbei.

188
00:14:12,790 --> 00:14:14,240
Tuanku mencapai kemenangan besar
di kota Lin,

189
00:14:14,240 --> 00:14:17,150
kenapa tuanku tak meraikannya
bersama para panglima dan tentera?

190
00:14:17,150 --> 00:14:18,720
Awak dah nampak Chu?

191
00:14:19,440 --> 00:14:20,110
Apa?

192
00:14:20,720 --> 00:14:21,920
Saya nampak dia tadi.

193
00:14:23,630 --> 00:14:25,030
Dia pun datang ke kota Lin

194
00:14:25,370 --> 00:14:27,080
dan selamatkan He Xiao.

195
00:14:28,080 --> 00:14:29,270
Tuanku nampak dia?

196
00:14:29,720 --> 00:14:31,520
Kalau awak nampak dia lain kali,

197
00:14:32,030 --> 00:14:33,750
awak mesti bawa dia balik.

198
00:14:35,320 --> 00:14:37,720
Jika tak boleh bawa dia balik hidup-hidup,

199
00:14:39,080 --> 00:14:40,480
bawa mayatnya pun boleh.

200
00:14:40,840 --> 00:14:41,480
Tuanku...

201
00:14:43,790 --> 00:14:45,790
Bukankah awak selalu nak bunuh dia?

202
00:15:04,390 --> 00:15:05,990
Rasanya tiada apa-apa, kan?

203
00:15:06,840 --> 00:15:07,510
Rasanya...

204
00:15:08,630 --> 00:15:09,830
Rasanya tak apa-apa.

205
00:15:10,910 --> 00:15:11,790
Rasanya?

206
00:15:12,510 --> 00:15:13,550
Awak ingat saya tak tahu?

207
00:15:13,550 --> 00:15:15,510
Selepas dua jam
makan eliksir pulih tenaga,

208
00:15:15,510 --> 00:15:16,550
tenaga dalaman akan pulih,

209
00:15:16,550 --> 00:15:17,720
tapi akan memendekkan jangka hayat.

210
00:15:17,720 --> 00:15:19,120
Awak beritahu saya tiada apa-apa?

211
00:15:19,120 --> 00:15:19,620
Ini...

212
00:15:20,600 --> 00:15:21,390
Ini bukan salah sayalah,

213
00:15:21,390 --> 00:15:22,240
Tuan Zhuge yang berkeras...

214
00:15:22,240 --> 00:15:22,840
Xing Er,

215
00:15:23,270 --> 00:15:24,400
saya yang paksa dia.

216
00:15:24,780 --> 00:15:27,510
Saya mesti pergi menyelamatkan awak
ketika itu.

217
00:15:28,440 --> 00:15:29,120
Xing Er.

218
00:15:40,910 --> 00:15:41,600
Xing Er,

219
00:15:42,360 --> 00:15:43,000
ini saya.

220
00:15:45,030 --> 00:15:46,430
Awak cari saya untuk apa?

221
00:15:47,120 --> 00:15:48,650
Saya cuma nak beritahu awak

222
00:15:49,080 --> 00:15:51,270
semua perkara yang
telah berlaku selama ini.

223
00:15:51,270 --> 00:15:53,000
Saya dah tak nak tahu sekarang,

224
00:15:53,220 --> 00:15:54,080
awak pergilah.

225
00:16:18,380 --> 00:16:18,970
Minum.

226
00:16:22,790 --> 00:16:23,720
Tak sangka

227
00:16:24,200 --> 00:16:25,360
saya dapat minum arak

228
00:16:25,360 --> 00:16:26,870
yang begitu lazat ketika saya masih hidup.

229
00:16:26,870 --> 00:16:28,390
Selepas tuan muda jatuh
ke dalam tasik ais,

230
00:16:28,390 --> 00:16:31,120
Pusat Gunung Hijau hantar
Tentera Pengawal Yue ke barisan hadapan.

231
00:16:31,120 --> 00:16:33,720
Ramai Tentera Pengawal Yue
yang terkorban dan cedera.

232
00:16:33,720 --> 00:16:36,320
Yang jadi tawanan perang
pula banyak diseksa.

233
00:16:37,200 --> 00:16:38,360
Siapa sangka

234
00:16:38,630 --> 00:16:40,270
kita masih dapat jumpa tuan muda lagi

235
00:16:40,270 --> 00:16:42,930
dan dapat makan daging
serta minum arak di sini.

236
00:16:42,990 --> 00:16:43,870
Bersulang demi kita yang masih hidup.

237
00:16:43,870 --> 00:16:44,600
Minum habis!

238
00:16:50,460 --> 00:16:51,480
Arak yang begitu lazat,

239
00:16:51,480 --> 00:16:54,150
macam mana boleh minum tanpa saya,
Fang Miaomiao?

240
00:16:54,150 --> 00:16:55,670
Macam mana awak buat begitu?

241
00:16:55,670 --> 00:16:56,670
Cawan arak dah ada dalam tangan awak

242
00:16:56,670 --> 00:16:58,470
sebelum saya sempat bertindak.

243
00:16:58,600 --> 00:17:00,200
Saya dah nampak tadi.

244
00:17:00,480 --> 00:17:02,390
Cik Fang digelar Pencuri Hebat,

245
00:17:02,670 --> 00:17:05,670
