537
00:34:11,469 --> 00:34:14,600
Maksud awak, Chu Qiao telah hilang
tanpa dapat dikesan?

538
00:34:15,030 --> 00:34:15,670
Ya.

539
00:34:17,020 --> 00:34:20,150
Patik risau dia akan
menjejaskan rancangan besar kita.

540
00:34:25,639 --> 00:34:27,889
Kalau begitu, kita serang dulu.

541
00:34:28,360 --> 00:34:29,440
Cepat bertindak

542
00:34:30,400 --> 00:34:32,400
