543
00:34:32,600 --> 00:34:33,590
Selagi kita dapat buktikan Putera Mahkota

544
00:34:33,590 --> 00:34:36,320
bersalah atas tuduhan bersubahat
dengan musuh,

545
00:34:37,170 --> 00:34:38,830
biarpun ada sepuluh Chu Qiao,

546
00:34:39,360 --> 00:34:41,489
dia tetap takkan dapat diselamatkan.

547
00:34:46,429 --> 00:34:48,949
Hari ini tanggal enam, kan?

548
00:34:56,030 --> 00:34:57,290
Hari ini tanggal enam.

549
00:34:57,400 --> 00:34:59,130
Kereta kuda telah disediakan?

550
00:34:59,470 --> 00:35:00,320
Tuanku,

551
00:35:00,400 --> 00:35:02,920
