558
00:35:13,960 --> 00:35:14,690
Tak mengapa.

559
00:35:14,840 --> 00:35:16,570
Berangkat ke Tokong Tianlong.

560
00:35:16,670 --> 00:35:17,630
Tuanku!

561
00:35:20,960 --> 00:35:21,550
Tuanku,

562
00:35:21,670 --> 00:35:24,070
