575
00:35:53,760 --> 00:35:54,800
Apa maksud awak?

576
00:36:05,840 --> 00:36:06,880
Ampun, tuanku.

577
00:36:06,910 --> 00:36:08,310
Ampun, Yang Berbahagia.

578
00:36:16,010 --> 00:36:18,070
Mana maharani? Kenapa tak jumpa dia?

579
00:36:19,400 --> 00:36:20,230
Maharani...

580
00:36:20,480 --> 00:36:22,280
Maharani sedang beristirahat.

581
00:36:24,070 --> 00:36:25,070
Hamba tak guna.

582
00:36:56,070 --> 00:36:56,760
Dinda.

583
00:36:57,620 --> 00:37:00,070
